lyrics:
[verse]
Kids running free, laughter fills the air
Imagination soaring, without a single care
Their smiles radiate, like the sun's warm embrace
In their playful world, every moment's a chase

[chorus]
Write a song, celebrating their innocence so pure
Their joy and laughter, an eternal allure
Kids playing, hearts just soaring high
In their carefree world, dreams touch the sky
